<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <title>Password Reset Email</title>
</head>
<body>
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" valign="top" style="background-color: #838383;"><br><br>
                <table width="600" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" valign="top" bgcolor="#d3be6c"
                            style="background-color: beige; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #000000; padding: 0px 15px 10px 15px;">
                            <div style="font-size: 48px; color: #6699CC;">
                                <br>
                                <b>Reset Your Password</b>
                            </div>
                            <div style="font-size: 24px; color: #6699CC;">
                                <br> You have requested to reset your password. <br>
                            </div>
                            <div style="color: black;">
                                <br> To reset your password, click the link below: <br> <br>
                                <a href="${resetLink}" style="background-color: #6699CC; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 5px;">Reset Password</a><br><br>
                                If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.<br><br>
                                Thank you,<br>
                                BIZZMATCH
                            </div>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table><br><br>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
